## System Requirements

- **Python:** 3.10 or higher
- **Operating System:** Windows 10+, macOS 12+, or Linux (Ubuntu 20.04+)
- **RAM:** 4GB minimum (8GB recommended for GPU acceleration)
- **Disk Space:** 1GB for installation

